Class Identifier

      • pulse.tasks.Identifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<NumericProperty>, Property
    public class Identifier
extends NumericProperty

    An Identifier is used to identify SearchTasks. It stores the internal task ID as its integer value and the last recorded ID.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      Identifier()
      Creates an Identifier by incrementing the previously recorded ID.
